pr_title: [ISSUE #119, #121] CN and EN content of documents of different release versions
pr_body:
CN and EN content of documents of different release versions

- [x] Different version classification implementation
- [x] Document content modification
- [x] Add a running illustration inside the Quick Start
- [x] Consistent content in both English and Chinese versions
- [x] Translation of documents not translated into Chinese
- [x] Version last updated to 1.9.0
- [x] Related or fixed issues #121 #122 #90 #119
